{"article_id":"KQLHMi0jJlUkBZos","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"U.S. military `` continues to refine options ''","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"says a senior defense official","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"German minister says","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"Russia , China blocked U.N. Security Council resolution","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Syria is urged to give a U.N. chemical weapons inspection team access to the site","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Al-Assad government says","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"claims","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"it used chemical weapons","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"are `` completely baseless ''","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"The United Nations and the United States are calling for an immediate investigation of Syrian activists ' claims","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"that the Bashar al-Assad government used chemical weapons in an attack on civilians .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"Anti-regime activist groups in Syria say","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"more than 1,300 people were killed in the attack outside Damascus , many of them women and children .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Video footage and witness reports appeared to bolster claims","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"that chemical weapons were used .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"President Barack Obama has directed the U.S. intelligence community to urgently gather additional information","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"to try to assess","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"whether chemical weapons were used Wednesday ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"State Department spokeswoman Jen Psaki said Thursday .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"At this time ,","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"she said ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"the United States is unable to `` conclusively determine '' chemical weapons use ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"but is focused on trying to nail down the facts , along with its international partners .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"Psaki said ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"as she has before ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"if reports of chemical weapons use prove true ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"the president has a range of options","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"available to him","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"to respond .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Did Syria cross a red line ?","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"Did Syria cross a red line ?","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"07:53","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"More chemical weapons use in Syria ?","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"MUST WATCH More chemical weapons use in Syria ?","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"02:24","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"See how U.S. might help Syrians","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"See how U.S. might help Syrians","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"01:42","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"CNN on the ground in Damascus","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"MUST WATCH CNN on the ground in Damascus 04:38","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"Later , a senior defense official told CNN","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"that `` the military continues to refine options","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"for Syria","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"to be prepared for whatever the president might request down the line . ''","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"Psaki noted","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"that Secretary of State John Kerry spoke by phone Thursday to Syrian opposition leader Ahmad Jarba ; U.N. Secretary-General Ban Ki-Moon ; and French , Jordanian , Turkish and European Union leaders .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Ban Ki-moon said","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"the alleged incidents Wednesday need to be probed `` without delay . ''","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Ban urged a Damascus-based team `` to be granted permission and access","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"to swiftly investigate the incident ''","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"and the United Nations is sending a formal request to Syria .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"`` He expects to receive a positive response without delay , ''","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"his spokesperson said in a statement .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"U.N. High Commissioner for Human Rights Navi Pillay said","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"the matter is `` of utmost urgency ''","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"and the `` allegations are exceptionally grave . ''","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"Pillay urged both the government and opposition to enable investigators `` to examine the site of the alleged attacks without any delay or obfuscation . '' `` The use of chemical weapons is prohibited under customary international law , ''","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"she said ,","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"noting","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"that the prohibition is binding on the government and rebels .","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"`` Whether or not chemical weapons were in fact used ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"it seems that once again in Syria many civilians have been killed in flagrant contravention of international law . ''","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"U.N. special advisers Adama Dieng and Jennifer Welsh similarly urged immediate access for the U.N. investigation .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"JUST WATCHED White House under pressure","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"MUST WATCH White House under pressure","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"02:12","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"Rebels :","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"Assad using chemical weapons","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"MUST WATCH Rebels :","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"Assad using chemical weapons","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"01:17","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"Reports of a new chemical attack in Syria","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"Reports of a new chemical attack in Syria","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"02:18","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"`` There is never any military justification for the use of chemical weapons","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"-- whether by governments or anti-government armed groups --","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"given their horrific and indiscriminate impact , ''","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"they said in a joint statement .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"The reports prompted international outrage ,","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"with a U.N. Security Council briefing called late Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"to discuss the situation .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"However , Russia and China","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"-- consistent allies of the Syrian government --","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"reportedly blocked a formal resolution .","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"Hours after the closed-door meeting , French Foreign Minister Laurent Fabius told CNN affiliate BFMTV","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"that `` a reaction of force must be taken ''","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"if the allegations are true .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"`` If the U.N. Security Council can not do it ,","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"decisions will be made otherwise , ''","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"Fabius said .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"But ,","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"he said ,","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"sending ground troops to Syria is out of question .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"Fabius also added his voice to calls for a U.N. team","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"currently in Syria","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"to investigate previous claims of chemical weapons use by either side","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"to be given access to the site of the alleged massacre outside Damascus .","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"If al-Assad 's regime `` has nothing","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"to reproach itself with , ''","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"it should let the U.N. weapons inspectors investigate the alleged attack ,","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"Fabius said .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"`` If the Syrians refuse ,","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"that means they have been caught red-handed , ''","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"Speaking on a visit to Berlin ,","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"Turkish Foreign Minister Ahmet Davutoglu called on the United Nations to act decisively ,","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"Turkey 's semi-official Anadolu news agency reported .","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"Davutoglu said","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"`` all red lines '' have been crossed","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"without the United Nations taking action in Syria","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"and that the body `` ca n't assume an undecisive attitude about chemical weapon attacks '' there .","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"`` If the Syrian regime is confident enough ,","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"it should allow the U.N. team to investigate","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"( the chemical attack claims )","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"immediately , ''","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"he added .","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"Speaking alongside him ,","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"German Foreign Minister Guido Westerwelle said","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"the reports from Syria `` are serious","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"and ,","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"should they be confirmed ,","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"outrageous . ''","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"He demanded a prompt explanation of the reported chemical weapons use ,","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"and also called for the U.N. chemical weapons team to be allowed access .","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"`` I regret","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"that Russia and China have blocked a formal resolution of the Security Council , ''","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"Westerwelle said .","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"Al-Assad 's government denied the claims on state-run media Wednesday ,","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"calling them `` completely baseless . '' `` Everything","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"that has been said","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"is absurd , primitive , illogical and fabricated , ''","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"said Syrian Information Minister Omran Zoabi on state TV .","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"the claim was timed by the opposition","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"to coincide with the U.N team 's visit","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"and came","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"as government forces were making gains on all sides against the rebels .","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"CNN could not immediately verify","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"where or when the videos were recorded ,","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"and could not authenticate the number","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"killed or injured .","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"Yuval Steinitz , Israeli Minister of Strategic Affairs , told Israel Radio on Thursday morning","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"that its intelligence assessments indicated","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"that `` chemical weapons were used ,","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"and they were not used for the first time . ''","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"He accused the international community of `` paying lip service ''","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"when it comes to Syria .","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"`` Nothing practical , significant , has been done in the last two years","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"in order to stop the continuing massacre of civilians","depth":13},{"id":167,"text":"carried out by the Assad regime , ''","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"`` I think","depth":11},{"id":170,"text":"that the investigation of the United Nations is a joke . ''","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"The White House said Wednesday","depth":5},{"id":172,"text":"that officials were `` working urgently","depth":6},{"id":173,"text":"to gather additional information . ''","depth":6},{"id":174,"text":"It called for the U.N. team in Syria to be given immediate access to witnesses and affected individuals ,","depth":6},{"id":175,"text":"and to be allowed to collect evidence unhindered by the government .","depth":6},{"id":176,"text":"`` If the Syrian government has nothing to hide","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"and is truly committed to an impartial and credible investigation of chemical weapons use in Syria ,","depth":8},{"id":178,"text":"it will facilitate the U.N. team 's immediate and unfettered access to this site , ''","depth":7},{"id":179,"text":"the statement said .","depth":6},{"id":180,"text":"But U.S. senator and former presidential candidate John McCain was strongly critical of the administration 's handling of the situation in an interview with CNN 's `` New Day '' on Thursday .","depth":5},{"id":181,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":182,"text":"chemical weapons use was `` obvious from the pictures","depth":8},{"id":183,"text":"when you see the dead bodies of children and women and others stacked up . ''","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"McCain said","depth":7},{"id":185,"text":"he was `` sure and confident ''","depth":9},{"id":186,"text":"that al-Assad had used chemical weaponry before ,","depth":9},{"id":187,"text":"and that Barack Obama 's failure","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"to act on what the U.S. president had said would be a `` red line ''","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"had given the Syrian leader a green light","depth":10},{"id":190,"text":"to use these weapons again .","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"McCain called for the United States to take military action from outside Syria 's borders","depth":6},{"id":192,"text":"to prevent that happening ,","depth":6},{"id":193,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":194,"text":"it could `` very easily '' do what 's needed","depth":7},{"id":195,"text":"to take out Syrian runways and aircraft","depth":8},{"id":196,"text":"and establish a no-fly zone .","depth":8},{"id":197,"text":"The Syrian civil war has killed more than 100,000 people","depth":5},{"id":198,"text":"and displaced millions ,","depth":5},{"id":199,"text":"according to the United Nations .","depth":4},{"id":200,"text":"There have been repeated allegations","depth":5},{"id":201,"text":"that chemical weapons were being used during the course of the conflict .","depth":5},{"id":202,"text":"The latest alleged attack took place in eastern and western Ghouta , rebel strongholds","depth":5},{"id":203,"text":"that the regime has been fighting","depth":6},{"id":204,"text":"to take back for more than a year .","depth":6},{"id":205,"text":"Initially , Syrian opposition groups claimed","depth":6},{"id":206,"text":"that hundreds were killed Wednesday ,","depth":6},{"id":207,"text":"but","depth":6},{"id":208,"text":"as the day wore on ,","depth":8},{"id":209,"text":"the number went up","depth":9},{"id":210,"text":"-- more than 1,300 people ,","depth":9},{"id":211,"text":"according to the opposition Local Coordination Committees and the Syrian National Council .","depth":8},{"id":212,"text":"The council is an umbrella group of anti-regime activists .","depth":8},{"id":213,"text":"Video","depth":9},{"id":214,"text":"posted Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":215,"text":"shows people carrying limp bodies ,","depth":9},{"id":216,"text":"some haphazardly covered in sheets ,","depth":10},{"id":217,"text":"others splayed , nearly nude , on the floor .","depth":10},{"id":218,"text":"A man is on his back ,","depth":10},{"id":219,"text":"staring blankly upward ,","depth":10},{"id":220,"text":"his chest convulsing violently .","depth":9},{"id":221,"text":"Others hold tissues to their mouth ,","depth":9},{"id":222,"text":"appearing to gag .","depth":9},{"id":223,"text":"Dr. Abu Said at a field hospital in Sakba , east of Damascus , told CNN","depth":9},{"id":224,"text":"how the injured started streaming in shortly after predawn prayers Wednesday .","depth":9},{"id":225,"text":"Forty of the 200 people","depth":11},{"id":226,"text":"brought to the field hospital","depth":11},{"id":227,"text":"died ,","depth":10},{"id":228,"text":"Said said .","depth":9},{"id":229,"text":"A man","depth":10},{"id":230,"text":"who referred to himself as a volunteer first responder ,","depth":10},{"id":231,"text":"Abu Gazi , said","depth":9},{"id":232,"text":"he was with a doctor at a field hospital in Arbeen","depth":10},{"id":233,"text":"who reported 300 people dead and 500 wounded .","depth":10},{"id":234,"text":"The symptoms ,","depth":12},{"id":235,"text":"he said ,","depth":12},{"id":236,"text":"included unconsciousness , foaming from the nose and mouth , constricted pupils , fast heartbeat and difficulty breathing .","depth":11},{"id":237,"text":"People died of asphyxiation ,","depth":11},{"id":238,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":239,"text":"`` The inspectors will not come , ''","depth":7},{"id":240,"text":"said a resident","depth":8},{"id":241,"text":"who did n't want his name used .","depth":8},{"id":242,"text":"`` If they wanted to come ,","depth":9},{"id":243,"text":"they would have come a long time ago . `` The Assad regime determines where the inspectors go ,","depth":9},{"id":244,"text":"and they will not let them go there .","depth":8},{"id":245,"text":"There is already a siege around eastern Ghouta from the Assad regime . ''","depth":7},{"id":246,"text":"Rights group Human Rights Watch also called Wednesday for the U.N. inspection team to be given immediate access to the area .","depth":5},{"id":247,"text":"`` Whether or not chemical weapons were used ,","depth":9},{"id":248,"text":"the attack left a large number of civilians dead ,","depth":9},{"id":249,"text":"and those responsible for unlawful killings should be held to account , ''","depth":8},{"id":250,"text":"it said .","depth":7},{"id":251,"text":"U.N. children 's agency UNICEF said","depth":7},{"id":252,"text":"the reports of Wednesday 's attack on civilians were deeply disturbing","depth":8},{"id":253,"text":"and that those","depth":10},{"id":254,"text":"who failed to protect children","depth":10},{"id":255,"text":"must be held accountable .","depth":9},{"id":256,"text":"Syria 's official news agency , SANA , quoted Iranian Foreign Minister Mohammad Javad Zarif on Thursday","depth":6},{"id":257,"text":"as saying","depth":7},{"id":258,"text":"the rebels must be behind any chemical weapons attack ,","depth":9},{"id":259,"text":"if confirmed ,","depth":9},{"id":260,"text":"as `` they do not hesitate to commit any crime . ''","depth":8},{"id":261,"text":"Russian officials , meanwhile , dismissed the claims of chemical weapons as a `` provocation","depth":8},{"id":262,"text":"planned in advance , ''","depth":8},{"id":263,"text":"Russian Foreign Ministry spokesman Alexander Lukashevich told Interfax news agency .","depth":7},{"id":264,"text":"He suggested","depth":7},{"id":265,"text":"it was timed","depth":8},{"id":266,"text":"to coincide with the visit by the U.N. team .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":533,"left":463,"right":532,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":463,"left":437,"right":462,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":437,"left":297,"right":436,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":297,"left":276,"right":296,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":269,"right":275,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":0,"right":268,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":268,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":271,"right":274,"relation":"